{"tid":1437781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"❢ ❢ ❢ ❢ ❢ 睇黎大家都唔記得左自己既初心了，送終條例仍然未暫停咁大單野都冇人理 ❢ ❢ ❢ ❢ ❢","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:43:19.000Z","uid":810,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c2e96611ada1318e3fb77fe03564c8c7ad8ca1","tid":1437781,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"緊急：政府講大話 送終條例仍然未暫停 大家睇吓截至7月31日 討論事務入邊仍然存在這一個法案  <a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192332/cs320192332999.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20192332%2Fcs320192332999.pdf&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=42b8af72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192332/cs320192332999.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kxm0vi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxm0vi1.jpg&h=67af6014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即係話依家既成果同一開始6月9號係完全冇分別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以推返啲緊要既post<br />\n機場呀，送終條例呀<br />\n其他唔慣事既就善用不推文回覆啦好嗎求下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e43a1bccf2bf0876c7cb284a70476bbb6433944","tid":1437781,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761d64cdefe34dbdd4e0a4d1c2def3d06eabd37e","tid":1437781,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ed1382221f0a63a6322004b5d9ff99cb5d561e","tid":1437781,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f